=================================================================== Filter cells based on various QC metrics (`scanpy.pp.filter_cells`) ===================================================================
For instance, only keep cells with at least `min_counts` and at most `max_counts` UMI and/or at least `min_genes` expressed genes and/or at most `max_mito_percent` mitocondria expression. This is to filter measurement outliers, i.e., "unreliable" observations.
